{"tid":1583292,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"最近咁多白衫打人點算?你呢個問題問得真係好...","createTime":"2019-09-20T14:01:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T23:53:07.000Z","uid":273621,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f7594229f3639d215f0ccc7b19911acb4fb218ef","tid":1583292,"uid":273621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T14:01:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你呢個問題問得真係好,<br />\n而我亦都好樂意解答你呢個問題。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6pmef4n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6pmef4n.jpg&h=4165c7a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢班火箭兵團成日周圍打人,唔可以放過佢地。<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2sY8kv3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2sY8kv3.jpg&h=8abfff09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n就決定用你啦,<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>獅鳥</strong></span></span>! 使出雙倍奉還!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y27tkv6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy27tkv6.gif&h=d826c029&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不過打還打,老規矩,<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>失去戰鬥能力</strong></span>就好收手喇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D4rayXt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD4rayXt.png&h=0511c750&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">「藍黃是政見,黑白是良知」</span></strong>,<br />\n人地揀錯隊都唔好是非不分。<br />\n仲有千祈唔好阻住喬伊小姐救人!!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FyWxNa6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFyWxNa6.jpg&h=556f86c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n未見喬伊小姐出現,可以考慮使用波波球。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u8hXYhN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu8hXYhN.jpg&h=14862fc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔係叫你唱歌啊....<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WgAbihK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWgAbihK.jpg&h=79380f58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n係要將火箭兵團既罪狀<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">寫出黎</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5VhpDhL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5VhpDhL.jpg&h=0d006d6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n寫比全世界知佢地做左咩衰野,<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">如果唔係外國會以為你人多蝦人少,無啦啦打人架。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BU3PPpo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBU3PPpo.png&h=c724c5a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GozWupq.pg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGozWupq.pg&h=e1f69e38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果對方派出<strong>戴魯比</strong>或者<strong>黑魯加</strong>點算?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e8k29po.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe8k29po.png&h=396f812b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n唔洗驚,我地用<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">水伊貝</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZYhEsa4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZYhEsa4.png&h=8da0c9f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n除左水剋火之外,水伊貝仲可以 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">Be Water</span></strong></span>,避開對方既攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NLoTwPj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNLoTwPj.png&h=307b08dc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"e1d59b0b3b487234710a90126f71e236cbd34431","tid":1583292,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T14:02:34.000Z","msg":"[公海 文宣整合] 9.29全球反極權集會 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581746\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1581746</a><br />\